text:
With the holidays almost here, we had to know what Christmas is like at the Roja’s residence. “Well, we hang out with the family, it’s pretty basic, honestly. Every aunt brings a dish, we all just party, we all just take shots. We listen to music, we do tournaments with video games with my cousins.

Read more: http://www.eonline.com/news/899663/here-s-how-prince-royce-does-christmas-shopping-for-girlfriend-emeraude-toubia
title: Here’s How Prince Royce Does Christmas Shopping for Girlfriend Emeraude Toubia
